<h1>Our Statement</h1>
<p>
<p>We hereby state that this data gathering session is conducted sorely for the purpose for a research study related to the citations in scholarly research papers. The data will be collected, and only be used for our research study. These annotations, as part of our research project, will be used to develop a tool that will hopefully make reading such research papers an easier task.</p>
